While writing a screenplay for his memoir , Blue Like Jazz , Donald Miller realized that his `` story '' was n't all that he wanted it to be . ||| 1
Even more , his life was n't everything that God intended . ||| 1
So , Miller set out to live a life that mattered -- to write a meaningful narrative . ||| 1
With the perfect blend of honesty , humor , and humble wisdom , A Million Miles inspires readers to create a new story -- a better story . ||| 1
To be a character who makes a difference and glorifies the Author . ||| 1
Last night , Andy and I heard Donald Miller speak about this book , when his A Million Miles tour came to Hollywood . ||| 1
He and Susan Isaacs did a great job . ||| 1
If the tour visits your city , do n't miss it . ||| 1
